dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Joe Carter. May I please have your name?
Hi there! My name is Judith White.
Nice to meet you, Judith! Could you kindly provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Yes, my policy number is five six two zero zero and my date of birth is zero four zero five nineteen eighty-seven.
Thank you for that information, Judith. Can you also confirm the make and model of the vehicle involved in the incident you're calling about today?
Of course, the vehicle is a two zero one five Honda Civic.
Great, thank you for providing those details. Is there anything else you would like to add or inquire about regarding your policy or claim?
No, that's all for now, thank you.
Thank you, Judith, for your time and cooperation today. Please don't hesitate to reach out if you have any further questions. Have a great day!
Thank you, Joe. You too, have a wonderful day!
